caption.title: Reduced levels of ROS affect the anti-dengue virus defense.
caption.p: A, Effect of treatment with ROS scavenger APO on DENV infection in the mosquito 10 days PBM (13 days post RNAi) (mean ± SEM). B, Effect of ROS inhibitor NAC treatment on DENV infection in the mosquito 10 days PBM (13 days post RNAi) (mean ± SEM). Student’s t-tests were used to determine the significance of difference in expression between treated and control groups. *** p<0.001. Each treatment group comprised 30 mosquitoes.
